Here is the translation:

Devotee of God, Vasram's name, this community of people in Kerar; 
Devotee of Hari, Valabai, worships Hari at Meghpur.

I do not set Shivaraj's son as my own; 
It is his great freedom that is my name; 
Countless divine feasts and worship I have in abundance.
